Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.74,0:03:51.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,司令 新联合国要求通信
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.42,0:03:56.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新联合国的潜水艇怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.84,0:04:00.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在仍紧跟在Alvis后方约50公里处
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.05,0:04:06.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要怎么处理呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.64,0:04:08.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接过来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.81,0:04:16.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来总算得到对话的机会了啊 API-1的各位
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.02,0:04:21.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是新联合国秘书长赫丝特·盖洛普
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.15,0:04:26.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是Alvis代表 真壁史彦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.66,0:04:28.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 真壁司令
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.99,0:04:34.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在当前这个战争时期 我们迫切希望和你们并肩作战
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.79,0:04:42.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为此 希望推行乐园计划的贵方能满足我们一个要求
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.79,0:04:42.09,ruby,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(564,1000)}Arcadian Project
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.22,0:04:45.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也有要求
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.01,0:04:46.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.01,0:04:52.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中止新联合国对本岛的一切干涉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.52,0:04:59.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真亏你说得出这么自私的话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.78,0:05:03.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拥有那么强大的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.90,0:05:07.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然不协助联合国
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.91,0:05:10.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你以为我们会容忍吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.79,0:05:14.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我拒绝呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.21,0:05:20.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真壁司令 你真的能拒绝吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.06,0:05:34.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于是 你同意了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.27,0:05:35.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.40,0:05:40.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把Mk.Ⅵ交给新联合国
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.77,0:05:42.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.11,0:05:47.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 也不想想我们花了多少年才完成啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.53,0:05:51.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在只能接受对方的条件
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.04,0:05:58.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新联合国的人类军运输舰队后天会到达我们Alvis
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.21,0:06:02.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把Mk.Ⅵ移动到向岛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.38,0:06:05.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们没时间消沉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.84,0:06:09.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抓紧去做Mk.Ⅲ和Mk.Ⅳ的最终调整
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.84,0:06:10.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.64,0:06:18.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新联合国到底为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.36,0:06:23.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难不成…！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.44,0:06:26.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得很有可能
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.53,0:06:29.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这件事远见医生知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.57,0:06:32.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还没告诉她
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.91,0:06:36.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 对方背后可能有个棘手的人物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.58,0:06:42.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最起码要把布伦希尔德系统的连接数据抽走
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.88,0:06:43.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.80,0:06:52.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身体要不要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.89,0:06:54.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事没事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.68,0:06:56.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.06,0:06:59.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托你 再等一会儿
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.77,0:07:02.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一骑同学应该很快就会来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.94,0:07:09.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皆城同学
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.66,0:07:12.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一骑同学还不来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.78,0:07:14.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.75,0:07:20.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,远见
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.08,0:07:21.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.29,0:07:24.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你手上还有粉笔灰
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.71,0:07:25.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.51,0:07:34.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皆城同学很关心你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.60,0:07:37.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没 没这回事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.82,0:07:49.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一骑 今天走那边
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.61,0:07:51.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶 为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.28,0:07:55.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,模拟战之前 先去做做上次的训练
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.79,0:07:58.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.50,0:08:07.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 坐在这种地方
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.17,0:08:10.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,春日井同学…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.84,0:08:15.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没事吧 脸色很差啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.10,0:08:17.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没这回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.18,0:08:19.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就好…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.90,0:08:26.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,羽佐间！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.52,0:08:27.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,翔子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.78,0:08:32.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该是轻微贫血
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.40,0:08:36.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系 这个不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.28,0:08:38.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.03,0:08:41.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思 春日井
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.83,0:08:45.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,翔子她好像太拼命了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.25,0:08:50.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,羽佐间她肯定是很喜欢现在的生活吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.47,0:08:55.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关于羽佐间翔子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.59,0:08:58.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,考虑到她的身体状况
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.22,0:09:02.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想让她暂时脱离计划
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.94,0:09:06.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能考虑一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.36,0:09:09.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.36,0:09:12.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是真壁司令的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.49,0:09:16.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是狩谷老师你的意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.66,0:09:20.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是乐园计划的方针
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.87,0:09:26.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,医生你也知道我们的时间不多了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.21,0:09:30.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这我倒是明白…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.38,0:09:32.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是她的病…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.13,0:09:36.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她的病是宿疾 对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.93,0:09:43.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在这个计划里牺牲了多少人？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.23,0:09:48.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事到如今还装什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.15,0:09:56.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你醒了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.82,0:10:00.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都再三嘱咐过你不能勉强了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.37,0:10:02.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.83,0:10:05.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身体没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.91,0:10:06.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.21,0:10:12.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈还有机库的工作 今晚你就在这儿休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.46,0:10:14.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.34,0:10:17.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也住下来陪你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.88,0:10:18.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.59,0:10:20.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也会陪着你的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.55,0:10:22.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.47,0:10:24.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.14,0:10:29.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我就去西尾奶奶那里买些好吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.31,0:10:30.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.86,0:10:36.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 妈妈就去工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.99,0:10:39.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真矢 就麻烦你照顾翔子了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.32,0:10:42.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的 慢走
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.95,0:10:44.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你 妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.87,0:10:49.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真矢 有件事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.00,0:10:50.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.75,0:10:52.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有件事想拜托你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.75,0:10:53.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.30,0:11:05.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然春日井说愿意帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.47,0:11:08.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是翔子说希望一骑也来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.65,0:11:12.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.40,0:11:14.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.73,0:11:16.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我过后去病房
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.19,0:11:19.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,…那样我也会更开心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.88,0:11:35.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐 轮到一骑同学了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.55,0:11:39.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唔 要抽哪张呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.84,0:11:42.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别磨蹭了 快抽吧
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(Part-B)
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.42,0:12:24.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最好别和他们走得太近
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.68,0:12:26.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总士…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.48,0:12:36.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你和他们 已经不能再做朋友了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.61,0:12:44.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.11,0:12:46.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.99,0:12:52.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也能像一骑同学那样开法芙娜吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.16,0:12:55.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等你好起来了就行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.38,0:13:00.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的身体会有好起来的那天吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.67,0:13:03.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然会有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.38,0:13:06.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可是健康的妈妈的女儿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.18,0:13:08.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.48,0:13:18.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神剑型…真想快些亲眼看看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.48,0:13:18.15,ruby,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(468,1000)}Nothung Model
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.48,0:13:18.15,tips,NTP,0,0,0,,注：典出「尼伯龙根的指环」中齐格飞所持的诺通宝剑 nothung的德语原意为「生于危难中」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.19,0:13:21.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它十分值得一看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.53,0:13:28.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所罗门发出预言
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.53,0:13:30.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出现位置在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.59,0:13:49.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秘书长 祝福者出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.55,0:13:50.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.39,0:13:56.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在那里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.27,0:14:04.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所罗门发出应答 类别为Ambivalent 断定为质问者型
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.27,0:14:04.65,ruby,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(808,1000)}矛盾
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.74,0:14:07.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麻烦你辅助通信了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.57,0:14:08.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.66,0:14:09.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要说「明白」才对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.49,0:14:11.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.16,0:14:12.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,远见
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.12,0:14:16.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,静下心来做就没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.75,0:14:17.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.67,0:14:19.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「静下心来」哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.06,0:14:42.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,护卫舰被击沉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.77,0:14:47.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都来到这里了 怎么能空手而归！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.86,0:14:51.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,司令 新联合国发来讯息要求救援
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.57,0:14:55.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是被击沉就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.70,0:14:58.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是也不能坐视不理
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.21,0:15:00.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让Mk.Ⅺ出击
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.75,0:15:02.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.09,0:15:09.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的身体还没好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.22,0:15:11.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.68,0:15:13.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.85,0:15:20.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也有工作
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.10,0:15:24.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帮助一骑同学是我的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.53,0:15:35.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有没有什么我能帮你的？羽佐间
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.29,0:15:39.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,春日井同学…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.46,0:15:44.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,法芙娜 启动进程就绪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.88,0:15:46.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,驾驶员请进入驾驶座
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.01,0:15:53.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即将到达法芙娜机库
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.64,0:15:57.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们到了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.86,0:16:06.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一骑同学
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.82,0:16:08.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,翔子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.03,0:16:12.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你又要出击了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.28,0:16:13.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.07,0:16:17.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要回到这个岛上来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.95,0:16:23.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时 我会在这里当助理
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.37,0:16:26.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你一定要回来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.59,0:16:27.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.05,0:16:33.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说定了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.72,0:16:43.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会保护你回来的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.90,0:16:45.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.52,0:16:49.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,LDA展开
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.65,0:16:51.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第1、第2固定栓 锁定
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.53,0:16:53.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第3、第4固定栓 锁定
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.86,0:16:55.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,法芙娜 移出机架
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.53,0:16:57.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,AVC飞龙 运至转盘
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.24,0:16:59.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,移动至转乘区
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.79,0:17:08.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最终安全装置检查 全部正常
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.54,0:17:10.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,法芙娜 已固定于连接位置
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.34,0:17:11.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连接臂 锁定
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.69,0:17:28.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次是救援行动
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.48,0:17:30.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们要去搭救新联合国的舰队
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.32,0:17:32.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是要去救人对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.01,0:17:58.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,API-1的救援还没来吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.85,0:18:08.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在那里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.03,0:18:22.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飞龙已到达运输舰队求援接触点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.62,0:18:26.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让医疗队待命 准备收治伤者
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.25,0:18:32.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会！所罗门又发出预言了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.79,0:18:34.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祝福者的出现位置在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.26,0:18:38.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龙宫岛正上方1万米处
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.63,0:18:41.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,立即将重力波防护罩展开到第2层
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.14,0:18:44.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全体岛民请立即到掩体内避难
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.27,0:18:49.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重复一遍 全体岛民请立即到掩体内避难
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.61,0:18:56.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第1重力波防护罩 正遭到波长干涉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.99,0:19:00.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,波长已被同步
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.66,0:19:04.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第1重力波防护罩被突破
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.58,0:19:07.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,距目标接触第2重力波防护罩还有2秒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.21,0:19:15.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第2重力波防护罩 要撑不住了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.71,0:19:19.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目标将剧烈撞击龙宫岛山顶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.97,0:19:21.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来不及测定质量
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.10,0:19:24.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准备迎接冲击
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.47,0:19:30.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目标降至本岛中央区域
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.77,0:19:32.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确认受损情况
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.44,0:19:33.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祝福者呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.52,0:19:37.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该是质问者型 但却是过去的资料里没有的类型
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.27,0:20:13.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,命令变更
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.48,0:20:15.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龙宫岛上出现了新的祝福者
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.40,0:20:18.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龙宫岛上有敌人？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.97,0:20:43.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一骑 马上回去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.84,0:20:44.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,办不到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.76,0:20:45.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,办不到也给我办！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.85,0:20:51.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第3、第5隔离壁启动
